      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"Hard to knock the form of 5. STRAIGHT TO THETOP who added to a string of wins and placings when third form this barrier at her latest appearance at Maryborough. Won the last time she raced here. Strong claims. 7. PARIS JAMILLA bombed the start when resuming but will be fitter for that and won her lone attempt at this circuit and distance. Improver. 2. ALWAYS SKYE HIGH came from this barrier for a good win at Bendigo two back then stepped up to a similar draw to this for third last time. Kept up to the mark with a trial win and a nice draw should ensure a cosy run. Manners can be a problem for 8. TIPPLE TIME but she draws for a trail and has some ability with her A-game.\",\"runners\":[5,7,2,8],\"exclusive\":false}",
